<view class='white-bg border-box padding-30'>
  <view class='font-30 margin-b black-color'>
    为何需要设置模板消息推送
  </view>
  <text class='font-24 gray-color'>
  由于微信小程序不支持主动下发模板消息，为了方便您及时收到外教沟通的消息，我们将通过微信公众号以即时消息方式向您推送，请按照以下步骤进行模板消息设置。
  </text>
</view>
<view class='white-bg margin-t-20'>
  <view class='padding-30 font-weight font-28 border-b-1'>
    第一步：绑定手机号
  </view>
  <view class='flex justify-between align-center border-box margin-t-30 margin-b-30 form'>
    <input bindinput='bindinput' class='input font-24 border-box' type='number' placeholder='请准确输入手机号' placeholder-class='font-24' maxlength='11'></input>
    <button bindtap='submit' class='submit flex justify-center align-center white-color font-24 theme-bg'>提交</button>
  </view>
  <view class='padding-lr-30 padding-b-30 font-24 black-color'>
    <text>已经参与过课程报名、学习需求提供过手机号的学生可不填</text>
  </view>
</view>
<view class='white-bg margin-t-20'>
  <view class='padding-30 font-weight font-28 border-b-1'>
    第二步：关注微信公众号
  </view>
  <view class='flex padding-30 justify-center font-24 align-center'>
    <view class='flex justify-between flex-direction'>
      <view class='two-top flex align-center justify-end'>
        <view class='flex justify-center align-center flex-direction'>
          <image mode='widthFix' class='image-point' src='/images/point.png'></image>
          <view class='flex align-center'>点击右上角【
            <image mode='widthFix' class='image-point-min' src='/images/point.png'></image>】</view>
        </view>
        <image mode='widthFix' class='image-right' src='/images/right-1.png'></image>
        <text>点击“关于FirstTutor”</text>
      </view>
      <view class='flex align-center'>
        <text>关注“FirstTutor”公众号</text>
        <image mode='widthFix' class='image-right image-left' src='/images/right-1.png'></image>
        <text>点击“相关公众号”</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <image mode='widthFix' class='two-image' src='/images/this.png'></image>
  </view>
</view>
<view class='white-bg margin-t-20'>
  <view class='padding-30 font-weight font-28 border-b-1'>
    第三步：进入微信公众号进行绑定
  </view>
  <view class='padding-30 font-24'>
    <text>点击微信公众号自定义菜单“学生绑定”进行学生手机号绑定（手机号要求与小程序端提供的手机号一致）。绑定成功后，您就可以即时收到外教的沟通信息了。</text>
  </view>
</view>